vergessene Aspekte der deutsch-polnischen Geschichte herausgearbeitet werden können.   aThis study explores the Polish image of Prussia in the second half of the 18th century, a period marked by the division of Poland and Lithuania and the loss of national independence, while at the same time, the apex of the Polish enlightenment. The author questions the prevalent notion of a strong negative image of Prussia in Poland and reveals forms of reciprocal cultural transfer and political relations.   aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 26. Aug 2020) 0aNational characteristics, Prussian. 4aAufklärung. 4aEnlightenment. 4aKulturtransfer. 4aPolish partitions. 4aPolish-Prussian relations. 4aPolnisch-preußische Beziehungen. 4aPolnische Teilungen. 4acultural transfer. 7aHISTORY / Modern / 18th Century.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus eBook-Package 2017z978311071954308iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2017z9783110540550oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE History 2017z9783110547764oZDB-23-DEG0 cEPUBz97831105186340 cprintz978311051833740uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978311052090340uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783110520903423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/covers/9783110520903.jpg  a978-3-11-071954-3  DG Plus eBook-Package 2017b2017  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_HICS  aEBA_DGALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-DEGb2017  aZDB-23-DGGb2017